org.mxupdate.install
Class InstallDataModel_mxJPO

java.lang.Object
  org.mxupdate.install.InstallDataModel_mxJPO

public class InstallDataModel_mxJPO
extends Object

Installs and updates the data model needed for MxUpdate. The JPO class is automatically called from the "MxInstall.mql" MQL installation script.

Method Detail

mxMain

public void mxMain(matrix.db.Context _context,
                   String... _args)
            throws Exception
Method used as entry from the MQL interface to install / update the data model for MxUpdate. The data model is installed / updated in this order:
  • install trigger group type
  • install trigger group policy
  • install trigger group relationship
  • update attributes in updateAttributes(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String, String, String, String, String)
  • update used business types by appending required MxUpdate attributes in updateBusTypes(ParameterCache_mxJPO)
  • define plug-in properties in makePluginProperty(ParameterCache_mxJPO, File)
  • register the MxUdpate Update programs with their symbolic names in registerPrograms(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String, String, String, String)
  • register MxUpdate as application in registerMxUpdate(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String)

Parameters:
_context - MX context for this request
_args - first value defines the source installation path (in development it is the resources sub directory), second value the version of MxUpdate which must be installed
Throws:
Exception - if installation failed
See Also:
installTriggerGroupType(ParameterCache_mxJPO, File, String, String, String, String, String, String), installTriggerGroupPolicy(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String, String, String, String, String), installTriggerGroupRelation(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String, String, String, String, String), updateAttributes(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String, String, String, String, String), updateBusTypes(ParameterCache_mxJPO), registerPrograms(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String, String, String, String), registerMxUpdate(ParameterCache_mxJPO, String, String), makePluginProperty(ParameterCache_mxJPO, File)

registerPrograms

protected void registerPrograms(ParameterCache_mxJPO _paramCache,
                                String _applName,
                                String _applVersion,
                                String _authorName,
                                String _installerName,
                                String _installedDate)
                         throws Exception
All programs evaluated with LIST_MXUPDATE_PROGRAMS are checked if they must be registered with a symbolic name and all other specific properties are set. If they are not already registered, the registration of the symbolic names of the programs are done. And also all other properties are set only if they are not already set.

Parameters:
_paramCache - parameter cache
_applName - used application name of the MxUpdate Update deployment tool
_applVersion - Mx Update version
_authorName - used author name
_installerName - used installer name
_installedDate - used installed date
Throws:
Exception - if registration of the symbolic names for all MxUpdate Update programs failed
See Also:
LIST_MXUPDATE_PROGRAMS

makePluginProperty

protected void makePluginProperty(ParameterCache_mxJPO _paramCache,
                                  File _sourcePath)
                           throws IOException,
                                  matrix.util.MatrixException
Creates and stores the properties for the plugin. A property entry is created for each type definition of TypeDef_mxJPO for which an icon (path) is defined. The format of the properties is defined in GetProperties_mxJPO.

Parameters:

_sourcePath - reference to the source path
Throws:
